## Model Selection

- Fast (Haiku-class): file scanning, discovery, docs generation, lint checks
- Standard (Sonnet-class): new features, use cases, tests, bug fixes — default
- Complex (Opus-class): architectural refactoring, cross-layer decisions, ADRs

## Safe Auto-Approvals

Auto-approve: read, search, diff, lint, build, test:unit
Require explicit approval: deps:install, DB migrations, deploy, seed, secrets, force push, destructive DB ops
